1. Convert file to UTF-8 and update any charset references.
1a. Add a symlink to include directory
2. Run decruft.py -> gives decruft.xhtml
3. Run bspsplit.py on decruft.xhtml -> gives skeleton.xhtml and bsps.xhtml
4. Edit skeleton.xhtml, using chromium audit to remove unused css
5. Run recombine.py on skeleton.xhtml and bsps.xhtml -> gives recombine.xhtml
6. Run html_curlify on recombine.xhtml
7. Sort out remaining {"} and {'}
8. Replace em-dashes with spaced en-dashes
9. Replace space between em-dash and closing quotes with nbsp.
10. Run prince.
